 erfect chance to soak up summer\, meet new people\, and enjoy the outdoors
 .\nNeed resources on river/water and sun safety as we kick off summer happ
 enings on campus? We got you covered!\nHosted in collaboration with the Of
 fice of Pluralism & Leadership and campus/community partners including Led
 yard Canoe Club\, Student Wellness\, 2028 Class Council and the First Gene
 ration Office. Free and open to all Dartmouth students\, staff and faculty
